└── password-generator-app
    ├── Dockerfile
    ├── requirements.txt
    └── web
        ├── app.py
        ├── password_generator.py
        └── templates
            └── index.html

Update and upgrade packages: 
  apt update && apt upgrade -y
  mkdir password-generator-app
  cd password-generator-app
  vim requirements.txt
  vim Dockerfile
  mkdir web
  cd web
  vim password_generator.py
  vim app.py
  mkdir templates
  cd templates
  vim index.html
